statements.sql: select SUM(CASE WHEN status = 1 THEN amount END) AS totalAmountReceived, SUM(CASE WHEN status = 1 THEN charge END) AS totalChargeReceived, SUM((CASE WHEN created_at >= CURDATE() AND status = 1 THEN amount END)) AS todayDeposit from `funds`

select COUNT(id) AS totalUser, count(CASE WHEN status = 1  THEN id END) AS activeUser, SUM(balance) AS totalUserBalance, COUNT((CASE WHEN created_at >= CURDATE()  THEN id END)) AS todayJoin from `users`

select count(CASE WHEN status = 3  THEN status END) AS closed, count(CASE WHEN status = 2  THEN status END) AS replied, count(CASE WHEN status = 1  THEN status END) AS answered, count(CASE WHEN status = 0  THEN status END) AS pending from `tickets` where `created_at` > '2022-08-21 12:21:24'
select sum(amount) as totalAmount, DATE_FORMAT(created_at,"Day %d") as date from `funds` where month(`created_at`) = '09' group by DATE(created_at)
select sum(amount) as totalAmount, DATE_FORMAT(created_at,"Day %d") as date from `funds` where month(`created_at`) = '09' and `status` = 1 group by DATE(created_at)

select SUM((CASE WHEN remarks LIKE "%Interest From%" THEN amount  END)) AS totalAmount, DATE_FORMAT(created_at,"Day %d") as date from `transactions` where month(`created_at`) = '09' group by DATE(created_at)
select sum(amount) as totalAmount, DATE_FORMAT(created_at,"Day %d") as date from `payout_logs` where month(`created_at`) = '09' and `status` = 2 group by DATE(created_at)

select COUNT(CASE WHEN status = 1  THEN id END) AS pending, SUM((CASE WHEN status = 2 AND created_at >= CURDATE()  THEN amount END)) AS todayPayoutAmount, SUM((CASE WHEN status = 2 AND created_at >=  DATE_SUB(CURRENT_DATE() , INTERVAL DAYOFMONTH(CURRENT_DATE)-1 DAY) THEN amount END)) AS monthlyPayoutAmount, SUM((CASE WHEN status = 2 AND created_at >=  DATE_SUB(CURRENT_DATE() , INTERVAL DAYOFMONTH(CURRENT_DATE)-1 DAY) THEN charge END)) AS monthlyPayoutCharge from `payout_logs`
select * from `users` order by `created_at` desc limit 5
